data.description: ***FARRAGUT SCHOOLS****Just reduced, in time for you to have a new home for the holidays!Lenoir City address but within the Knox county school district...Northshore  Elementary, Farragut Middle and Farragut High Schools!   This wonderful home is located close to all the perks of the Choto area...marinas, parks, walking trails and restaurants.  A large fenced back yard  perfect for family gatherings, lounging or bbqs.  Beautiful open kitchen with quartz counter tops and beautiful tiled back splash.  Seller is offering a $3,000 flooring allowance.  Optional pool membership available Great house in a great location!
